{"tid":1108354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中年女子屍浮維港","createTime":"2019-04-16T01:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T01:58:26.000Z","uid":3090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eaf9841c08cb6bf9abdd95c6d7e4a301f345de93","tid":1108354,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/60t5ROB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F60t5ROB.png&h=d54d5c0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FX6OPAh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFX6OPAh.png&h=0f86b052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目擊途人協助警員調查。李家傑攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n水警輪在現場搜索。李家傑攝<br />\n<br />\n上環信德中心對開海面，早上6時許，途人發現一名女子在海面隨水漂浮，水警及消防船趕至現場搜索，將一名中年女子撈起，她身體已嚴重發脹，由救護員送律敦治醫院，經醫生證實已告死亡，警方正展開調查。"},{"pid":"5cc63e2fe84504e910aadb8589e5e9febde8777f","tid":1108354,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:57:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67b30d86eb025d48c93bf37918cb2f9a6959039a","tid":1108354,"uid":30109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:58:26.000Z","msg":"@奶波魔魔"}]}